OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FEmergency government meetings have
OL,7,Fbeen held to prepare for a "worst-case
OL,8,Fscenario" if the war in Iran continues
OL,10,FWords by Suzanne Elliott
OL,12,FThe economic shock unleashed by the
OL,13,Fwar in the Middle East and the
OL,14,Fresulting closure of the critical
OL,15,Fwaterway, the Strait of Hormuz, has
OL,16,Freverberated around the world and
OL,17,Fcould further disrupt UK households.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
