PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FA leaked report to The Times on
OL,7,FThursday morning suggests the closure
OL,8,Fcould affect UK supermarket shelves,
OL,9,Fthe hospitality industry, and
OL,10,Fhealthcare this summer due to a
OL,11,Fshortage of carbon dioxide (CO2)
OL,12,Flinked to the conflict.
OL,14,FCO2 is crucial to the food and drinks
OL,15,Findustry, used to store packaged meats
OL,16,Fand salads and to carbonate drinks
OL,17,Fsuch as beer and soft drinks, as well
OL,18,Fas energy and healthcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FWhile ministers have sought to
OL,7,Freassure the public that supplies are
OL,8,Fnot currently at risk, contingency
OL,9,Fplans are being drawn up for a
OL,10,F"reasonable worst-case scenario".
OL,12,FSo how serious is the threat - and why
OL,13,Fis CO2 such a vital part of the
OL,14,Feconomy? ITV News explains.
OL,16,FWhy is CO2 a crucial part of the
OL,17,Feconomy?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
