CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FCarbon dioxide (CO2) is usually only
OL,7,Fspoken of in terms of its negative
OL,8,Feffects on the climate, but it plays a
OL,9,Fcrucial role in many industries - from
OL,10,Fhealth and hospitality, to food and
OL,11,Ffarming.
OL,13,FCO2 is used in meat and poultry
OL,14,Fproduction as a tool for stunning
OL,15,Fanimals for a more "humane" slaughter
OL,16,Fand for keeping food fresh in transit
OL,17,Fby preventing microbial growth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FIt is widely used by the food and
OL,7,Fdrink industry as it can be
OL,8,Ftransported safely and does not affect
OL,9,Fthe flavour or texture of the food it
OL,10,Fis protecting.
OL,12,FMost visibly, CO2 makes carbonated
OL,13,Fdrinks - from cola to beer - fizzy,
OL,14,Fbut it is also a vital component in
OL,15,Fbags of salad, which typically contain
OL,16,Fa high amount of CO2 (15%) that
OL,17,Fprevents the leaves from browning too
OL,18,Fquickly, and in meat packaging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776380581
OL,3,CWhat a CO2 shortage in the UK means
OL,4,Cfor food, healthcare and hospitality
OL,6,FThe gas is also needed to make dry
OL,7,Fice, used to transport temperature-
OL,8,Fsensitive foods in the post, an issue
OL,9,Fthat is unlikely to impact UK food
OL,10,Fsupplies significantly, but could
OL,11,Faffect smaller production.
OL,13,FIt is also used in water purification,
OL,14,Fand, slightly less urgently, CO2 is
OL,15,Fwhat creates the holes in crumpets.
OL,17,FOutside the food industry, CO2 has
OL,18,Fother critical uses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
